trans-unit.source: Contains a type and a collection of values associated with that type.
This class corresponds to an ASN.1 structure defined in the Cryptographic Message Syntax standards specification.

Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.CryptographicAttributeObject"></xref> class using an attribute represented by the specified <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Oid"></xref> object.
The attribute to store in this <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.CryptographicAttributeObject"></xref> object.

Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.CryptographicAttributeObject"></xref> class using an attribute represented by the specified <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Oid"></xref> object and the set of values associated with that attribute represented by the specified <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.AsnEncodedDataCollection"></xref> collection.
The attribute to store in this <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.CryptographicAttributeObject"></xref> object.
The set of values associated with the attribute represented by the oid parameter.
Gets the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Oid"></xref> object that specifies the object identifier for the attribute.
The object identifier for the attribute.
Gets the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.AsnEncodedDataCollection"></xref> collection that contains the set of values that are associated with the attribute.
The set of values that is associated with the attribute.
